<subSubSection pageId="10" pageNumber="35" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="10" pageNumber="35">Culture characteristics.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="10" pageNumber="35">
<taxonomicName genus="Colonies" lsidName="Colonies" pageId="10" pageNumber="35" rank="genus">Colonies</taxonomicName>
on PDA (Figure 2, PE25), superficial, initially white with flat mycelium on media, later becoming dark, circular, flossy and velvety; reverse dark. Not sporulating in culture.
</paragraph>
